<div class="page-header">
<h3>User Control Page!</h3>
<p>Below is the user interface for you to use LabAS3's RESTful API to create a user.</p>
</div>

<form action="/users/submit"  style="border:1px solid #ccc" method="POST">
  <div class="container">
    <h3>Create User</h3>
    <p>Please fill in this form to create a user.</p>
    <hr>

    <p><label><b>ID Number</b></label>
    <input type="num" placeholder="Enter ID#" name="id" required></p>

    <p><label><b>First Name</b></label>
    <input type="text" placeholder="Enter First Name" name="firstname" required></p>

    <p><label><b>Last Name</b></label>
    <input type="text" placeholder="Enter Last Name" name="lastname" required></p>

    <p>By creating a user you agree to adhere to our <a href="#" style="color:dodgerblue">Terms & Privacy Policy</a>.</p>

    <div class="btn-group">
      <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Create User (POST)</button>
      <button type="button" class="btn btn-info">Update User aka (PUT)</button>
      <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary">Delete User</button>
      <button type="button" class="btn btn-info">Cancel</button>
    </div>
    <br>
  </div>
</form>

